### Combobox con tabla estructurada:
```yaml
CmbNombre As combobox:
    BorderColor: =RGBA(226, 232, 240, 1)
    BorderThickness: =1
    DisplayFields: =["Value"]
    Height: =44
    InputTextPlaceholder: ="Selecciona..."
